📌RECIPE >> Corn Chowder 玉米濃湯
.
Mr Bear is a soup monster (think cookie monster), I am constantly being “harassed” into cooking his favourite tomato soup. Didn't feel like cooking the same thing over and over again so I made corn chowder instead. There was still soup to please the master, and I got to make something different.😄
.
熊先生是個湯怪，就是很愛很愛喝湯的那種怪獸，每次都要我煮番茄濃湯，也太無趣了。那天熊湯怪又吵著喝湯，就給他來個玉米濃湯吧。
.
⚠️食譜附在後面的照片裡
.
.

我喜歡這樣的濃湯，可以當正餐😋
Looks so delicious! 😋😋 Can't wait to try ur recipe, thx for sharing!
